  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Voltaren being a Non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drug (NSAID) drug may be used as a single
      drug therapy in otitis externa being both therapeutic and analgesic thus reducing consumption
      of oral analgesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      anticipated advantages are: reduction of inflammation and edema, no fungal overpopulation-
      when steroids are employed, contains boric acid as an ingredient, high safety profile, can be
      switched to antibiotic therapy later, can be used in conjunction wit steroids
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
